{"tid":2038373,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟今日抗爭係為咩","createTime":"2020-05-27T13:49:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-28T04:20:38.000Z","uid":108794,"like":84,"dislike":74,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"7e1c3d959eec30ff650a5f72a3a580d67e9bce92","tid":2038373,"uid":108794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T13:49:04.000Z","msg":"個個話為咗畫面<br />\n先唔講24號已經有畫面<br />\n明知港島極重狗都照衝過去<br />\n明知依家玩濫捕<br />\n試問可以有咩畫面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後出到嚟個畫面咪一大堆人坐喺度等被捕<br />\n失去前途，甚至要離開香港<br />\n歸根究抵點解仲咁多人肯出嚟，咪就係為咗爭口氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但為咗口氣而犧牲三百個人，仲係咪值得<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n堅持黃色經濟圈，堅持做國際戰線，為保命將傷害減到最少，會唔會先係現時嘅唯一出路<br />\n現上個人見解，有錯可屌"},{"pid":"2d71fa1ae2bad4f035f90f0975d3dc2c0e0e77dc","tid":2038373,"uid":110860,"like":42,"dislike":6,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T13:50:25.000Z","msg":"係唔係都會濫捕 唔關你出唔出事"},{"pid":"617f89ade444aa1ad918986f2ec0e48fd063cec8","tid":2038373,"uid":341986,"like":8,"dislike":14,"score":-6,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T13:50:46.000Z","msg":"日日喺屋企上Twitter傷亡一定少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43404df363da84655c9758a0c5d81cfd7c360a64","tid":2038373,"uid":55089,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T13:51:16.000Z","msg":"濫捕到連食lunch同放學都照拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5134f0e76aa4d97a96e901de38287ae161180b4f","tid":2038373,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T13:55:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">今日大畫面被補嗰啲值得調查下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望係諗多咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"461acf56cfdfdd3960481fba58e0963df170893b","tid":2038373,"uid":108794,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"617f89ade444